item.description:
Hi,

Let's climb for a little while. I'm afraid I have to leave at 9:00PM .... no dragging me off the walls this friday. And no drinks after (for me - I hope you all still do!). Note, I'll be there at 6:30 to get a little early start since I can't close the place.

Please note, you will need to pass a belay test if you are an experienced climber but new to the gym. You should also take a class at Metrorock if you have never climbed before. Please call the gym in advance to make arrangements. The gym also has a shuttle to the gym from the T - Wellington Station if you don't have a car.

Hope to see some of you then,
Susan
item.how_to_find_us: I'll be the gal at the picnic table in read pants, grey or white sweatshirt and brown hat if it is cold ...
item.why: To climb or not to climb, that my friends is the question.
item.name: End O' March Climb
